# 1) Copy to: supabase/secrets.local.env  (that path is gitignored)
# 2) Replace the placeholder below with your PKCS#8 PEM as ONE line, using \n where line breaks were:
#    SUBSCRIPTION_RENEWAL_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nMIIEvQIBADANBg...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----"
# 3) Run: npm run supabase:secrets:subscription-renewal
#
# PKCS#8 only (-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----). Convert: openssl pkcs8 -topk8 -inform PEM -in rsa.pem -outform PEM -nocrypt -out pkcs8.pem

SUBSCRIPTION_RENEWAL_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nPASTE_BASE64_BODY_HERE_WITH_BACKSLASH_N_BETWEEN_LINES\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----"

# Retail POS MTN/Airtel mobile money via Flutterwave Edge Functions.
# Set these before deploying/serving `flutterwave-mobile-money` and `flutterwave-mobile-money-webhook`.
FLW_SECRET_KEY="FLWSECK_TEST-or-live-key"
FLW_WEBHOOK_HASH="paste_flutterwave_verif_hash"
# FLW_BASE_URL="https://api.flutterwave.com/v3"
